    <Paragraph>The GroupBox control is a HeaderedContentControl that provides a titled container for user interface (UI) content. This topic introduces the <Run FontWeight="Bold">GroupBox</Run>
 control and provides a beginning example of its use.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph/>
    <Paragraph/>
